'''Percival Chaplin''' (born 2000) is an English engineer and the eldest child of Air Force chief [[Hugo Chaplin]] and police officer [[Leilah Abdel]].

==Early life and education==
Percy was born in 2000 in Swansea, the first child of Chaplin and Abdel. 

